10.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp While watching the flying car scene from &quot;Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets&quot;, you suddenly jump up and yell &quot;Masquerade breach! Masquerade breach!&quot; and expect the people around you to know what your talking about.<br>
<br>
9.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp You wake up at 4 am in the morning because you had a nightmare that a Gangrel Alastor just ripped you to pieces with his feral claws.<br>
<br>
8.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When you walk out into the street and see a samurai, a lunatic, and an over-grown puppy dog fighting an eight-foot tall demon, you smile and somehow take it as an affirmation that you do indeed have a role to play in the world. <br>
<br>
7.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When a relative or friend tells you they're pregnant, you ask them if they received permission from their Sire and local Prince, first.<br>
<br>
6.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When lifting a heavy package, you declare yourself &quot;Brawny&quot; enough to move the box from Point A to Point B. <br>
<br>
5.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When the box starts to slip from your hands, you immediately burn a Willpower point to retest.<br>
<br>
4.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When playing hide and seek, rather than run and hide some place, you continue to stand in the exact same place you started with your arms crossed over your chest. When your opponent opens his eyes and moves to tag you, you declare: &quot;I'm in Obfuscate. You don't know I'm here.&quot;<br>
<br>
3.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When the person your watching TV with gets up to go to the bathroom, you lunge for the remote and announce &quot;I declare Praxis!&quot; <br>
<br>
2.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp When your parent / roommate / significant other asks why you didn't take out the garbage, you insist the vile Tremere Usurpers erased the chore from your mind.<br>
<br>
